	    the bass line, a steady four-four beat straight out of 
	    middle school band class.^^To the north is an open 
	    doorway, and a closed door is south; the hallway returns 
	    to the landing to the east.",
	e_to second_hallway,
	s_to second_hallway_end_door,
	n_to second_bedroom;

